snippet.title: Wastelander Closed Beta Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Wastelander is an upcoming indie basebuilding game with roguelike elements.

Currently in closed beta; Wastelander will be available on Steam by Summer 2023

Wishlist us at: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1688350/Wastelander/
